# Build outputs — nothing built is tracked. `bun run build` regenerates all of
# it: tsc → dist/, copy:lib → site/public/lib/ (the Pages demos import this
# local copy), docs → site/src/generated/, vite → site-dist/. The .skill bundle
# + its staging dir come from scripts/package-skill.ts; the skill bundles no
# lib copy — its templates import the published npm package from esm.sh.
